init_text:
Once upon a time there was an old mother pig who had one hundred little pigs and not enough food to feed them. So when they were old enough, she sent them out into the world to seek their fortunes. You know the story about the first three little pigs. This is a story about the 92nd little pig.

The 92nd little pig built a house out of depleted uranium. And the wolf was like, "dude."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So the wolf went up to the house and knocked on the door.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The little pig went to the kitchen and made a sandwich.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf opened the door and walked into the house.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: went to the kitchen and made himself a sandwich.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was turning into a frog.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She opened the door and said, "Oh, you're a frog now.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She opened the door and the frog hopped out.
